[SN]TITLE[SN]
Jean McConville's son, Michael, recalls her abduction

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Michael McConville was 11 years old when his mother, Jean, was abducted from her home in west Belfast. Her body was found more than 30 years later on a beach in County Louth.

